WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:04.950
Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.950
Well, Diana's behind the camera today,

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:08.710
and I have a word for you. So, I'm going

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:10.230
to tell you all some things that have

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:12.709
been on my heart. I got my Amazon

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:15.110
order in. I love to feed my squirrels.

00:00:15.110 --> 00:00:15.120
I

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:16.870
love to feed squirrels and I love to

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:19.349
watch them. I told Diana, I

00:00:19.359 --> 00:00:20.710
said, "I'm going to go out and

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:22.550
get the squirrels'food all

00:00:22.550 --> 00:00:22.560
around."I

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:24.470
was putting it all inside

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:26.470
the feeders. And the Lord spoke to

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:27.429
me and he said to me,

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:29.669
"Brandon, you like to watch

00:00:29.679 --> 00:00:32.630
the squirrels."And he said, "I like to

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:35.670
watch you. I like to watch my kids. I

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:38.310
like to bless my kids."And he

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:40.790
said, "Brandon, the squirrels didn't

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.510
earn the food. They didn't deserve the

00:00:43.510 --> 00:00:43.520
food."He

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.229
said, "It was grace that you

00:00:46.239 --> 00:00:48.709
did this today for them."And he said,

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:51.029
"What's about to happen in these last

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:53.910
days is going to be my grace poured out

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.869
on the people with finances."And he

00:00:56.879 --> 00:00:59.430
goes, "It will be to people that you

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:01.590
don't feel in your heart when I tell you

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:05.189
to give to somebody a big money.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:07.510
They don't treat you right.

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:09.590
They didn't act like they like you,

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.390
but it wasn't about you. It

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.550
was about me just blessing them through

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:17.749
you. As long as you can keep your eyes

00:01:17.759 --> 00:01:21.270
focused on me and attract to deflect,

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:23.830
I'll work through

00:01:23.830 --> 00:01:23.840
you."He

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:27.429
said to me,

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:30.149
"It's not always that they deserve it,

00:01:30.159 --> 00:01:32.870
and it's not always that they earned it.

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.670
It's just grace. And it's not because

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:38.710
they treated you right or they

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:42.069
treated you wrong."He said, "You

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:44.789
give secretly

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:47.749
and I'll reward you openly. The bigger

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:52.710
the checks I tell you to give,

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:54.870
the more it is to die to self because I

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:58.870
will not share my glory with anyone.

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:02.230
It's always

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:04.230
when

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:07.030
you lay hands on somebody in the days

00:02:07.030 --> 00:02:07.040
ahead

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:10.550
and they get healed from cancer

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:13.430
or diabetes, and instantaneously they're

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:16.309
like, 'You're my new best

00:02:16.309 --> 00:02:16.319
friend,'right?

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:18.630
Because you laid hands on them and it

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.750
solved a problem that was killing them,

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:24.550
but it had nothing to do with you. You

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:26.869
are just the person that God used to

00:02:26.879 --> 00:02:29.910
distribute the glory, right?

00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:32.150
The anointing of his presence

00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:34.229
destroys the yoke, but it has nothing to

00:02:34.239 --> 00:02:36.630
do with you. You're just a vessel. So,

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:39.190
it's the same way about the finances.

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:41.509
The Lord said to me, 'I'll not share my

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:44.229
glory with anyone concerning healing,

00:02:44.239 --> 00:02:46.630
and I'll not share at this level of

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:49.270
where I'm taking certain people with

00:02:49.270 --> 00:02:49.280
finances.'And

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:55.350
he said, 'One percent, Brandon, one

00:02:55.350 --> 00:02:55.360
percent

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.509
will walk in this end-time wealth of

00:02:57.519 --> 00:02:58.949
this kind of wealth that I'm talking

00:02:58.949 --> 00:02:58.959
about.'And

00:02:58.959 --> 00:03:00.790
I've brought that up before

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:03.110
to you all and told you about the one

00:03:03.110 --> 00:03:03.120
percent.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:07.190
But I'm talking about extreme wealth,

00:03:07.200 --> 00:03:10.070
extreme wealth, like more than

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:12.229
deca-millionaires.

00:03:12.239 --> 00:03:13.589
I'm not talking about you got a couple

00:03:13.599 --> 00:03:14.949
hundred thousand dollars in the bank

00:03:14.959 --> 00:03:16.710
and you're going, 'Well, you know, I'm

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:19.350
able to have extra in my...'That's not

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:21.350
extreme wealth. That's not like lavish,

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:23.990
like where you go, 'Wow,'to

00:03:23.990 --> 00:03:24.000
the world's

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:25.430
standards when the world's looking at

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:27.750
you and going, 'What is going on?

00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:27.760
How—what

00:03:27.760 --> 00:03:29.750
are they got going on with them?'It's all

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:32.630
about Jesus, you know what I'm saying? You

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:35.110
attract to deflect, and this is what it

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.589
will be with finances. And he told me it

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:40.149
will be as precise as listening to him

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:41.910
as a clock ticks

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:44.710
to listen for when he tells you to

00:03:44.720 --> 00:03:46.789
invest in something. When I talked about

00:03:46.799 --> 00:03:49.589
the pillars, listening to what those

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:52.390
pillars are and when to invest in those

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:55.190
pillars and listening to him and saying,

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:57.509
'Father, not my will, but yours be

00:03:57.509 --> 00:03:57.519
done.'But

00:03:57.519 --> 00:03:59.910
it's all about being

00:03:59.910 --> 00:03:59.920
like—I

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:04.070
want to call it a secret assassin.

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:06.070
You're mysterious.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:08.789
You walk in and you do the job. You

00:04:08.799 --> 00:04:11.509
do the mission for

00:04:11.519 --> 00:04:13.429
the government of the Lord. You want to

00:04:13.439 --> 00:04:15.429
say it's cool. In the government of the

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:17.590
Lord, you are an ambassador of the Lord.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.749
You work for him. You're doing exactly

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:22.550
what he's told you to do. You're his

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.629
hands. You're his feet. You're

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:26.790
maneuvering. You're moving

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:29.670
in that circumstance, and you drop it

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:32.790
and you get out, and it's all about him.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:34.870
So they're wondering

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:36.469
what happened, what in

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:38.390
the world went on. The glory came and we

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:39.749
don't even know what happened. It

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:41.430
changed the whole atmosphere. The

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:43.909
healing power of God came in. He said,

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:45.909
'Be made whole,'like I was talking

00:04:45.919 --> 00:04:48.629
about spirit, soul, and body—the whole

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:50.310
man. It's not just about healing. He

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:51.830
said, 'I'm going to use people for

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:54.790
healings and to restore back what the

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:57.830
cankerworm ate. But I'm not going to

00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:00.629
share my glory with anyone, Brandon, in

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:02.230
these last days. And if you can work

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:04.950
with me like that, we'll work great

00:05:04.950 --> 00:05:04.960
together.'Just

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:07.590
like the squirrels, they

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:09.670
don't even know when the food's coming,

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.670
but I pour the food in there and I just

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:14.150
like to watch them. They're so excited.

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.430
They run down the tree and they're

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:16.870
eating and they're filling their

00:05:16.870 --> 00:05:16.880
mouths

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:18.710
full. They don't even realize that

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.150
there was just grace that just happened.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:22.310
It was a grace explosion that all that

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:23.749
food was in that little

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:25.830
feeder. And they're going, 'Man, this is

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:27.670
so good.'And they take it and they

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:29.510
run off, and

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.550
they don't go and say,

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:32.150
'Thank you, sir,'you know,

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:34.550
waving from the branch.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:36.710
They just go, 'Man, I just had a really

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:38.629
good day. I don't know where all that

00:05:38.639 --> 00:05:40.710
came from, but it blessed my

00:05:40.710 --> 00:05:40.720
day.'And

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:42.790
watching that blessing blesses me.

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:44.629
And that's what he said. That's where

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:46.790
he's at. He just wants to see his kids

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:49.270
happy. He just wants to see his kids

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:51.270
happy and he's just loving on them. And

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:53.189
sometimes you just take and you put some

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:55.430
cash in somebody's hand or whatever.

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:57.270
Holy Ghost handshakes. 'How are you

00:05:57.280 --> 00:05:59.670
doing, brother? God bless you,'and just

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:00.870
walk away. And they don't even realize

00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:02.550
that you gave maybe a couple hundred

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:03.670
bucks or something. You know what I'm

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:07.029
saying? And you just flow that way. But

00:06:07.039 --> 00:06:09.350
the Lord was talking about how

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:11.430
whenever it comes down to healings and

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:13.590
demonstrations and the manifestations of

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:16.390
the glory, who is going to be

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:19.430
the elites of walking with him will

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:23.830
always be to attract the glory.

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:25.590
The presence of the Lord brings

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:28.309
the people to you, and then

00:06:28.319 --> 00:06:31.270
you push them to him. So I see

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:33.990
the squirrels as how

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:36.390
they're a blessing to me. And I know

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:38.309
that we are not squirrels; we're his

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:40.150
kids. But he was using it as something

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:43.110
to instruct me that day, is that he

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:44.790
said, 'Brandon, I just want you to

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:47.510
know there'll be one percent that flows in this

00:06:47.510 --> 00:06:47.520
end-time

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:49.909
wealth transfer of the great

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:52.629
wealth. And I'll not share my glory,

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:54.150
just like I won't share my glory

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:55.909
whenever you pray for somebody and they

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:57.510
try to say, "Thank you, sir."No, it

00:06:57.520 --> 00:07:01.110
ain't you. I'm just a vessel. We got to

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:03.110
always keep the main thing the main

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:05.189
thing and give God praise for

00:07:05.199 --> 00:07:07.670
everything in these last days. We have

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:09.670
to always be looking at his face and

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:11.589
knowing that he is the rewarder of those

00:07:11.599 --> 00:07:14.870
that diligently seek him, not Brandon. I

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:17.430
may write a check. I may be the

00:07:17.440 --> 00:07:19.270
distributor of the wealth that

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:23.110
he gave me, but it's always to give God

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.189
the praise. And it will be for the

00:07:25.199 --> 00:07:28.150
unlikely people. They may not treat you

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:29.430
right. You say, "I don't think they

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:31.189
treat me very good. I don't think

00:07:31.199 --> 00:07:33.749
they're very kind to me."And that's

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:35.270
usually probably the ones that he wants

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:36.710
to bless the most. That's why I

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:38.870
thought it was interesting

00:07:38.880 --> 00:07:40.390
about the healings, because he was talking

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:42.390
about you'll see healings on people that

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:44.870
are strung out on drugs, strung out, and

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:46.790
they're not the ones that are believing

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:48.150
and going over there in the corner

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:50.230
having all the Bible verses like sister

00:07:50.230 --> 00:07:50.240
so-and-so,

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:52.230
and she's all—and she

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.589
may be struggling with something. She

00:07:53.599 --> 00:07:55.909
might die by something. I don't know.

00:07:55.919 --> 00:07:58.950
It's not my job to test the hearts.

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:02.070
All I do is obey. And you go and

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:03.830
he'll say, "Pray for that lady right

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.350
there on the side of the road,"and she

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:07.510
could be a hooker. And the power of

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:09.830
God hits her and you go, "My God, she

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:11.589
had a creative

00:08:11.599 --> 00:08:14.390
miracle!"And

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:16.790
it was just something she didn't

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:19.589
earn and something she didn't deserve.

00:08:19.599 --> 00:08:21.749
It's called grace. And that's exactly

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:24.070
who He is, a God of grace, and He is a

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:26.070
God of love. And you didn't earn

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:28.469
salvation and you didn't deserve

00:08:28.479 --> 00:08:30.950
salvation, but it's just His grace. And

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:33.589
He said, 'I love you and I've provided a

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:35.430
way for you that you don't have to go to

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:37.110
hell today.'I'm trying to tell you

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.230
that's what He's talking about: the

00:08:38.230 --> 00:08:38.240
end-time

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:41.029
wealth transfer of what's about to

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:43.670
happen with the finances. It's something

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:45.350
you can't earn and it's something you

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:47.030
don't deserve, but God said, 'I'm going

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:50.310
to bless you.'And I've seen what's

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:53.910
about to happen again with a glimpse.

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:56.150
As I was lying in bed, I could see over

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:58.230
and I was looking into these

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:01.110
months ahead of what God is trying to do

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:03.269
just for His remnant,

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:05.750
for the people who He just

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:07.430
wants to watch and see. It's

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:10.710
like when you go on Christmas morning

00:09:10.720 --> 00:09:12.949
and you've given your kids all these

00:09:12.959 --> 00:09:14.550
beautiful presents and you're excited

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:16.550
just to see their expression of the

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:18.550
package that you've wrapped up in a bow,

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:20.870
and they're going to go, 'Daddy, look at

00:09:20.880 --> 00:09:23.430
what you got me today!'and they're so

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:25.430
excited and celebrating that present

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:27.990
that they got. And that's what He's

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:31.190
looking at, as a good daddy, for healings

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:35.509
and blessings. And He's going,

00:09:35.519 --> 00:09:38.230
'I know, I just love my

00:09:38.230 --> 00:09:38.240
kids.'You

00:09:38.240 --> 00:09:39.990
know what I'm saying?

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.829
When you love your kids, you just do

00:09:41.839 --> 00:09:43.590
good things for them. And that's why it even

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:45.190
goes to Scripture. It says, 'If we,

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:47.030
being evil, give good gifts to our kids,

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:48.870
how much more does our heavenly Father

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:51.509
give good gifts to those that love

00:09:51.509 --> 00:09:51.519
Him?'And

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:53.430
I just know that my Daddy's a good

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:56.150
daddy. He's a God that rewards those

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:58.070
that diligently seek Him today. And I

00:09:58.080 --> 00:10:01.269
thought, as I watch my

00:10:01.269 --> 00:10:01.279
squirrels—I

00:10:01.279 --> 00:10:03.110
don't want to be a squirrel, but I

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.670
want to be a kid that is

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:08.310
just innocently seeking Him and

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:10.389
being hungry after even the corn,

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:12.870
saying, 'Man, I'm just so thankful that

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:15.509
He blessed me today.'So if He asks you

00:10:15.519 --> 00:10:17.590
to give a check to somebody or asks you

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.269
to pray for somebody that you don't feel

00:10:19.279 --> 00:10:21.750
like deserves it,

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:23.430
it's just God saying, 'I just want to

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:25.910
give them a hug today.'It's something

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:27.910
they didn't earn and it's something they

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:30.470
didn't deserve. But sometimes He may ask

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:32.310
you to do something that's uncomfortable

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:33.670
to your flesh, and you think, 'Well, I'd

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:35.590
like to give it to the lady that's over

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:37.110
here that's been praying a lot or

00:10:37.110 --> 00:10:37.120
whatever,'but

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:38.710
He's just wanting to love

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:40.630
on the unlovelies.

