01:20:07.199 --> 01:20:08.870
all this stuff, but he wants us to have

01:20:08.880 --> 01:20:12.470
fun and enjoy ourselves. So that's what I

01:20:12.480 --> 01:20:14.310
have for y'all today. God bless you all,

01:20:14.320 --> 01:20:16.870
and thank you for joining me. Remember,

01:20:16.880 --> 01:20:19.669
put a smile on your face and a song in

01:20:19.679 --> 01:20:21.830
your heart. Jesus loves you so much and

01:20:21.840 --> 01:20:23.350
we love you. God bless you and we'll see

01:20:23.360 --> 01:20:26.960
you again soon. Bye-bye.

